Description:
Grateful to return to @uofwaterloo not just as an alumnus, but as a voice for the #NextGeneration. Being the speaker at the 2025 Grad Class Send-Off brought back memories, pride, and purpose. Stay tuned for the 🎬
#UWaterloo #GradSendOff #Changemaker #SDGLeaderhsip 

@waterloomath @uwaterlooalumni @uwmathsoc

A truly humbling moment—receiving a token of appreciation from the Dean after sharing my journey with the next generation of changemakers at @uofwaterloo. Grateful to be back where it all began, and proud to give back to a place that gave me so much.

#UWaterloo #FullCircle #Gratitude #ProudAlum 
@waterloomath @uwaterlooalumni @uwmathsoc
